[I] Touch Typing Tutor

[T] KTouch is a typewriter trainer for learning to touch type. It provides you
[T] with text to train on and adjusts to different levels depending on how good
[T] you are. It displays your keyboard and indicates which key to press next
[T] and which is the correct finger to use.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/ktouch/

